#lem: Etarsirsir[1]TN; banšur[table]; X; dalla[(to be) bright]; e[leave]
#etcsl: line-id=B.33

B.34. nin di kud ka-aš bar mu dug₄-ge X-me-en
#lem: nin[lady]; did[lawsuit]; kud[separate]; kaš[decision]; bar[place outside]; mu[name]; dug[speak]; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.34

B.35. si sa₂ diŋir-re-ne-me-en dam ur-saŋ-ŋa₂-me-en
