#etcsl: line-id=B.36

B.37. {d}ba-u₂ nin di kud <ka-aš bar mu dug₄-ge X-me-en>
#lem: Bau[1]DN; nin[lady]; did[lawsuit]; kud[separate]; kaš[decision]; bar[place outside]; mu[name]; dug[speak]; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.37

B.38. si sa₂ <diŋir-re-ne-me-en dam ur-saŋ-ŋa₂-me-en>
#lem: si[horn]; sa[equal]; diŋir[deity]; dam[spouse]; ursaŋ[warrior]
